<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ARA Release: {{ release.release_title }} - volume {{ release.release_volume }} </title>
    <style>
        /* --- Basic Reset & Typography --- */
        :root {
            --primary-color: #0d47a1; /* A deep, professional blue */
            --text-color: #333;
            --light-gray: #f4f4f4;
            --border-color: #ddd;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fff;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        /* --- Layout --- */
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 2em auto;
            padding: 0 2em;
        }

        /* --- Header --- */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding-bottom: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 2.5em;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #666;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .header h2 {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0.2em 0;
            line-height: 1.2;
            color: #000;
        }
        .header .release-date {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 0.5em;
        }
        .header .download-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.8em 1.5em;
            margin-top: 1.5em;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }
        .header .download-button:hover {
            background-color: #0b3a82;
        }

        /* --- Main Content Sections --- */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 2.5em;
        }
        .section h3 {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding-bottom: 0.5em;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        .about-box {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 0.1em 1.5em;
        }

        /* --- Table of Contents Article List --- */
        .toc-article {
            margin-bottom: 2em;
            padding-bottom: 2em;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .toc-article:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .toc-article h4 {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            margin: 0 0 0.2em 0;
        }
        .toc-article .authors {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
        }
        .toc-article .abstract {
            font-size: 0.95em;
            color: #444;
        }
        .toc-article .links {
            margin-top: 1em;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .toc-article .links a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 1.5em;
        }
        .toc-article .links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* --- Footer --- */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 4em;
            padding-top: 1.5em;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #888;
        }

        /* --- Responsive Layout --- */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 1em auto;
                padding: 0 1em;
            }
            .header h2 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
        }
        
        /* --- Classy Print Styles --- */
        @media print {
            body {
                font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
                color: #000;
            }
            .container {
                max-width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }
            .header .download-button, .footer {
                display: none;
            }
            .header, .section {
                border: none;
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
            h1, h2, h3, h4 {
                color: #000 !important;
            }
            .about-box {
                background: #eee;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
            }
            a {
                color: #000;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        
        <header class="header">
            <h1>Amateur Research Association</h1>
	    <h2>{{ release.release_title }} - volume {{release.release_volume}}</h2>
            <p class="release-date">Published: {{ release.publication_date }}</p>
            <a href="{{ release.release_volume }}.pdf" class="download-button">[under construction]Download Full Volume PDF</a>
        </header>

        <main>
            <section class="section about-box">
                <h3>About this Project</h3>
                <p>
                    The Amateur Research Association (ARA) is an experimental publishing platform designed for independent researchers, citizen scientists, and industry professionals. Our mission is to provide a venue for high-quality, unaffiliated research that combines (almost, hopefully) the legitimacy of a formal journal with the accessibility of a preprint server.
                </p>
                <p>
                    This release was produced using an automated, open-source workflow. All submissions are typeset in LaTeX, managed via GitHub, and compiled into a cohesive volume. For more information, please see our foundational whitepaper included in this issue.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="section">
                <h3>Table of Contents</h3>

                {% for item in content_list %}
                    <article class="toc-article">
                        <h4>{{ item.metadata.title }}</h4>
                        <p class="authors">
                            {% for author in item.metadata.authors %}
                                {{ author.name }}{% if not loop.last %}; {% endif %}
                            {% endfor %}
                        </p>
                        {% if item.metadata.abstract %}
                        <p class="abstract">{{ item.metadata.abstract }}</p>
                        {% endif %}
			{# CC licence probably?#}
			<p>Free full text access - supporting open research</p>
                        <div class="links">
                            <a href="{{ item.metadata.permalink }}.html">Metadata Page</a>
                            <a href="{{ item.metadata.permalink }}.pdf">Download PDF</a>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                {% endfor %}

            </section>
        </main>

        <footer class="footer">
            <p>
                Published by the Amateur Research Association. Contributions are licensed individually by their respective authors.
            </p>
        </footer>

    </div>

</body>
</html>

